
Jahia Rest API Tutorial source code V1.0
========================================

Requirements
------------

- A Jahia 6.6 or more recent installation

Documentation
-------------

This project is actually part of a tutorial available here : 
https://www.jahia.com/cms/home/download/jahia-academy/jahias-blog/blog-posts/fun-with-jahias-rest-api-tutoria.html

Installation
------------

To install, simply copy the rest.html file into the tomcat/webapps/ROOT directory of your existing Jahia installation

Run
---

Simply connect to http://localhost:8080/rest.html and then test the code by logging with any user, or if
you haven't created any users yet you can use the root login.
